<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="188017" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">赞同和感谢，傻傻分不清楚。<br>反对和没有帮助，傻傻分不清楚。</div>


